Build a TCL Tk utility that I will use with Tanner S-Edit

It will get currently viewed cellview's library, cellname and viewname using

workspace getactive -library
workspace getactive -cell
workspace getactive -view

Then, if the viewtype (obtained using: workspace getactive -type) is "symbol", it will show the command that will be executed, for user to review:

cell renameview -library LIB_NAME -cell CELL_NAME -view VIEW_NAME -newname symbol

The window has two buttons : Proceed and Cancel.
